<div class="request-modal request-delete-modal" id="request-delete-modal" aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="request-modal__dialog request-delete-modal__dialog" role="dialog" aria-modal="true" aria-labelledby="request-delete-modal-title">
    <button class="request-modal__close request-delete-modal__close" type="button" aria-label="Закрыть">&times;</button>
    <h2 class="request-delete-modal__title" id="request-delete-modal-title">Удалить заявку?</h2>
    <p class="request-delete-modal__text" id="request-delete-modal-text">Заявка будет удалена без возможности восстановления.</p>
    <p class="request-delete-modal__message" id="request-delete-modal-message" hidden></p>
    <div class="request-delete-modal__actions">
      <button class="request-delete-modal__button request-delete-modal__button--cancel" type="button" id="request-delete-cancel">Отмена</button>
      <button class="request-delete-modal__button request-delete-modal__button--danger" type="button" id="request-delete-confirm">Удалить</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
